708048f-a.text:
Third Ave., at and adjoining the S.W. corner of 35th Street. Also shown is 35th Street, south side, west from Third Ave., to, but not including Lexington Aves. No. 522 Third Ave., at the S.W. corner of 35th Street, is a 3-story frame house. No. 162 East 35th Street, west of Third Ave., is a 2-story frame building also. The view shows the 25th Precinct Police Station at No. 160 East 35th Street, west of the S.W.
corner of Third Ave.
July 23, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.

708045f-a.text:

January 7, 1939
Somach Photo Service
New York City Tunnel Authority

708047f-a.text:
Nhird Avenue, east side, north from E. 35th Street. At the right is a modern apartment house bearing No. 201 E. 35th Street.
